'''機修工'''是指使用工具维护或修理[[机器|机器]]的工匠、熟练技工或[[技术员|技术员]]<ref>{{Cite book|title=1980 Census of Population: Classified Index of Industries and Occupations|publisher=U.S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of the Census|year=1982|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tLLhHHKEhE4C&pg=SL15-PA68|accessdate=December 18, 2017|page=O-68|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410100102/https://books.google.com/books?id=tLLhHHKEhE4C&pg=SL15-PA68|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多数機修工基本只擅長某一领域的機器<ref>{{Cite book|last=Henderson|first=C.J.|last2=Dolphin|first2=J.|last3=Fehl|first3=P.|last4=Davenport|first4=R.|title=Career Opportunities in the Armed Forces|publisher=Facts On File, Incorporated|series=Career Opportunities Series|year=2010|isbn=978-1-4381-1062-2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YfAzNoC9o2oC&pg=PA230|accessdate=December 18, 2017|page=230|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410100102/https://books.google.com/books?id=YfAzNoC9o2oC&pg=PA230|dead-url=no}}</ref>。機修工資質通常由行业协会或政府机构认证。机械师可根据其維修的机器类型分为两类，即重型機修工和轻型機修工。重型機修工主要維修大型机器或重型设备，如[[拖拉机|拖拉机]]和[[拖车|拖车]]，而轻型機修工主要維修较小的機器，如汽车发动机。

